        "body": "This PR updates the Tamil translation (`tm.ts`) to fully align with the latest English i18n source.\r\n\r\n✔ All missing keys added  \r\n✔ Incorrect keys removed  \r\n✔ Structure now 1:1 with `en.ts`  \r\n✔ Placeholders preserved (`{{tableName}}`, etc.)  \r\n✔ Improved natural Tamil wording  \r\n✔ Verified ES/TS build passes  \r\n\r\nThis makes the Tamil locale ready for production use.\r\n",
